{"tid":1007213,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)罪惡城1-2","createTime":"2019-02-03T15:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T19:29:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fd5e6287261ec4cd5b6468ac194aa3c8b3f0d1","tid":1007213,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=874a966c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=1175dbf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=7c4ec068\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/24/Sincityposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F24%2FSincityposter.jpg&h=afcb361d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d2/Sin-City-A-Dame-to-Kill-For-teaser-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd2%2FSin-City-A-Dame-to-Kill-For-teaser-poster.jpg&h=5ff2843f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.講述三個故事：Sin City，The Big Fat Kill和That Yellow Bastard。這三個故事都發生在一個虛構的城市&mdash;罪惡之城，而在這座城市中，主教大人、參議員、警察卻正是罪惡的根源。故事由米基&middot;洛克所扮演的醜陋的大塊頭Marv開始。他與漂亮女人歌迪發生了一夜情，歌迪的美貌與柔情令他有一種被救贖的感覺，並讓他第一次感受到來自女人的&ldquo;愛&rdquo;。但當MARV半夜驚醒，卻發現睡在身邊的歌迪已經被殺。他卻成警方追捕的對象。 MARY為抓住殺死歌迪的真兇，展開了復仇之旅<br />\n<br />\n2.新的故事將圍繞在南西&middot;克拉罕（Nancy Callahan，潔西卡&middot;艾巴飾演）上。根據米勒表示，劇情會交織出「A Dame To Kill For」中的內容，並且表現「南西全新的一面」。目前沒有更多的故事劇情透露，但法蘭克&middot;米勒也表達了想在電影中加入《萬惡城市》中的其他短篇故事，其中包括「Blue Eyes」，以及新角色戴莉雅..<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=629bdb60\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=d4a2a1dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109b2af6e67eefc9c1717b14a5770690c169ee75","tid":1007213,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a12b7587e7efd1c00b6ee4d9e4cb4e1b5460710","tid":1007213,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im